><a class=\"vt-p\" title=\"WPML\" href=\"http://wpml.org/\" target=\"_blank\">WPML</a> keeps adding new members to its <a class=\"vt-p\" title=\"Theme Compatibility\" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\" target=\"_blank\">Theme Compatibility list</a>, and today we are very happy to include these themes: <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/shell-lite\" target=\"_blank\">Shell lite</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/456theme-premium-responsive-site-template/3006973\" target=\"_blank\">456</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/flight-responsive-fullscreen-background-theme/3917050\" target=\"_blank\">Flight</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/koorsi-all-in-one-ecommerce-portfolio-blog/4034664\" target=\"_blank\">Koorsi</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/kallyas-responsive-multipurpose-template/3583938\" target=\"_blank\">Kallyas</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: you can test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/multilingual-compatibility-testing-tool/\">Multilingual Compatibility Testing Tool</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML. You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Shell Lite theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/shell-lite\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-108204\" title=\"shell-lite-theme\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shell-lite-theme.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Shell is a fully featured translation ready premium-like WordPress Theme. Shell is suitable for serious Bloggers as well as Business Owners because it is a CMS Theme with a fully customizable landing page which features proper SEO structure, Theme Options manageable content, call-to-action button and more.It is useful as a starting point for Theme Developers or users who need to save time when building Themes. Use Shell as your Parent Theme and expand your work via 10 built-in action hooks. Currently Shell offers three custom Templates: Blog, Sitemap and Full Width Page. Shell requires latest version of WordPress and Child Theme for any personal customizations.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/shell-lite\" target=\"_blank\">Download Shell Lite</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">456 theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/456theme-premium-responsive-site-template/3006973\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-108205\" title=\"456\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/456.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>456Theme is a premium responsive html/css site template, built on Skeleton grid system. 456Theme was designed to convey your message to your potential customers and online users. Its purpose is to increase the number of repeat customers. Build your own skin color just for a couple of minutes. One of the main features is the ability to choose the colors you want for your buttons, links and header background. 456Theme offers tons of options, a few tens patterns for background, 4 sets of premium icons developed by icondock.com, 5 premium plugins &amp; more.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/456theme-premium-responsive-site-template/3006973\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase 456</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Flight theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\