by about 50% (x2 faster) and some functionality that we&#8217;ve been long waiting for is finally working smoothly. However, a little bug related to RSS feed filtering caused Feedburner to send a bunch of news emails in all languages.</p>\n<p>So, we&#8217;re going to spend Monday fixing these issues, retest and then we can release.</p>\n<p>The new WPML release will bring:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Much improved performance (both in the WP admin and in public pages)</li>\n<li>Much greater robustness to the menu sync functionality</li>\n<li>Support for Google-compliant language codes in translation links</li>\n<li>A bunch of warnings and notices fixed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I&#8217;ll write again, with full details when it clears QA and ready to ship.</p>\n<p>Have a great weekend, and again, sorry for all these French and Chinese emails that we sent you.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"http://wpml.org/2013/03/sorry-for-the-chinese-newsletter-wpml-2-7-is-coming/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"Multilingual ready responsive WordPress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"http://wpml.org/2013/02/multilingual-ready-responsive-wordpress-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"http://wpml.org/2013/02/multilingual-ready-responsive-wordpress-themes/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 27 Feb 2013 17:44:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Compatibility Bulletin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"http://wpml.org/?p=107597\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:371:\"Responsiveness means that the website displays well on different screen sizes. If you want your site to display nicely on PCs, tablets and mobile phones, you&#8217;re actually looking for a responsive theme. Here are responsive WordPress themes that are all compatible with WPML. Enjoy! Vibe Themes Vibecom was designed mainly for Corporate websites, portfolios and [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dominykas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5480:\"<p><strong>Responsiveness means that the website displays well on different screen sizes. If you want your site to display nicely on PCs, tablets and mobile phones, you&#8217;re actually looking for a responsive theme.</strong></p>\n<p>Here are responsive WordPress themes that are all compatible with WPML.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Vibe Themes</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-104780\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/main-535x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"535\" height=\"1024\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>Vibecom was designed mainly for Corporate websites, portfolios and design agencies. The theme is developed over Twitter Bootstrap CSS framework and takes full advantage of the many great features and tools that come with Bootstrap.</p>\n<p>VibeCom boasts unique features such as Page Builder, Live Theme Customizer, an Advanced Options Panel, Exclusive VibeCom Sliders and Premium LayerSlider.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/user/VibeThemes\" target=\"_blank\">Vibe Themes</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mojo Themes</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107601\" title=\"big_screen\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/big_screen-296x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"296\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>Aegaeus theme puts a focus on attention to details. Every element is designed so it fits on every screen size. Even though the theme is packed with templates and shortcodes, all of them were designed with great care.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.mojo-themes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Mojo Themes</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Hermes Themes</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107605\" title=\"feature-responsive\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/feature-responsive-300x153.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>Hermes is optimized for hotel / motel / inn / b&amp;b sites. Due to their nature, tourism sites receive a significant amount of traffic from visitors on mobile devices. Therefor, a combination of responsive layout and travel-industry features, make this theme unique and attractive.</p>\n<p>Some fun facts about the use of mobile in the travel industry:<br />\n1. According to recent Expedia research, more than 65% of people who book a hotel room within 24 hours of checking in do so from a mobile device.<br />\n2. At the same time, Priceline increased their share of mobile business by 31% after creating a mobile-friendly version of their website.<br />\n3. When booking hotels on their mobile device, travelers use the mobile web three times more than mobile apps.<br />\n4. Over 40% of all online hotel reservations are done directly on the hotel&#8217;s website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.hermesthemes.com\" target=\"_blank\">Hermes Themes</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kriesi Themes</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107619\" title=\"backend\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/backend-300x196.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"196\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107617\" title=\"choices-med\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/choices-med-300x233.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107615\" title=\"angular-med\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/angular-med-300x233.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>Kriesi makes different themes for different purposes. Replete is an e-commerce theme. Angular a portfolio theme and Choices a clean business Theme.</p>\n<p>Kriesi themes are all built on a framework that works very well with WPML. Once you activate the plugin the theme options panel becomes multi-language enabled and you can save an option set for each language, simply by switching the language in your backend.</p>\n<p>This means that you can use different styling, logos, layout and menu structure for each language based on your needs.</p>\n<p>Together with responsive design, Kriesi&#8217;s themes are a great option for responsive multilingual WordPress sites.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.kriesi.at/\" target=\"_blank\">Kriesi Themes</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BizzThemes</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-107639\" title=\"bizz-cart-showcase-responsive\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/bizz-cart-showcase-responsive-300x171.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"171\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>BizzThemes make clean, flexible and customization-ready themes. BizCart theme is a responsive E-Commerce theme for WooCommerce. It allows to easily setup a web shop that displays great on PCs, tablets and mobile phones.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://bizzthemes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">BizzThemes</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://wpml.org/2013/02/multilingual-ready-responsive-wordpress-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s