 Chateau is an elegant WordPress theme designed for hotels, hostels, resorts, spas and other small businesses.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.hermesthemes.com/themes/royal-chateau/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Royal Chateau</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Gonzo theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/gonzo-clean-responsive-wp-magazine/2415788\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-94952\" title=\"dealicious\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/gonzo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Gonzo is built with semantic HTML5/CSS3 and is completely responsive. Not only is it responsive but it also keeps that magazine feel right down to mobile screen sizes. Practically every typographic element has been endlessly tweaked for different screen sizes to make sure it looks great no matter what the device.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/gonzo-clean-responsive-wp-magazine/2415788\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Gonzo</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BigBangWP theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bigbang-responsive-wordpress-template/2826493\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-94952\" title=\"dealicious\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/bigbang.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Responsive WordPress template. Instagram, Flickr, Dribbble &amp; Pinterest photostreams…</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bigbang-responsive-wordpress-template/2826493\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase BigBangWP</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs